inner-reflections/         <-- Root folder of your app
│
├─ index.html             <-- Home page with overview & main menu
├─ journal.html           <-- Daily Journal page (dialog to write entries)
├─ prompts.html           <-- Guided prompts page (text or inspiration)
├─ inspiration.html       <-- Tips & Inspiration page (quotes, book excerpts)
├─ relax.html             <-- Breath & relaxation exercises
├─ game.html              <-- Mini-game page (canvas + stars)
├─ entries.html           <-- Page to review saved journal entries
│
├─ style.css              <-- Styling for all pages (colors, fonts, buttons, layout)
├─ script.js              <-- JS for journal, menu highlight, mini-game
└─ README.md              <-- Optional, info about your project
